iness.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>   ... some states did not get federal aid.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>   ... federal laws did not apply to some roads.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>",
